        "created_at": "2016-01-01T22:12:28.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I am opening a 2004 Guy Roulot Meursault Vireuils.   It is from Vireuils Dessous if I am not mistaken.   Vines planted by Guy Roulot as a massale clone in the 1950s.</p>\n<p>Does anyone have any producers who produce wines from Vireuils Dessus?  What is the difference?</p>\n<p>I know this is a little geeky but there is a method to my madness here.</p>\n<p>Thanks!</p>",
